    "Some examples are random forest, classification and regression tree (CART).",
    "• Those algorithms that are based on the Bayesian technique are the ones that use the Bayes theorem and make it easier to use subjective probability in model development.",
    "The significant algorithms used for classification and regression problems are Nave Bayes and Bayesian Belief Network.",
    "• Pattern analysis is the basis of the kernel approach, which incorporates a wide range of mapping methods.",
    "Support vector machines (SVM) and linear discriminant analysis (LDA) are essential kernel approaches in ML modeling."
